data.description: Right on the beach, this superb vacation home has three floors of south-facing deck space hanging out over the dunes. It offers unparalleled views of the emerald Gulf of Mexico. Recently remodeled from the studs out, it has a new roof and professional interior decor. Paved parking at the front of the home provides ample space for four vehicles and direct access to the home. Two gulf-front bedrooms on the first level allow access to the lower deck and path to the beach. There's also a media room with a fridge and wet bar for young guests to hang out. The second floor reveals panoramic 180-degree gulf views from every corner of the living space through a wall of glass. Make yourself at home in this spacious family room which has a defined dining area and ample sitting space looking out over the emerald waters. Three sets of French doors deliver stunning gulf views along with access to the balcony. It's an amazing outdoor space for reading or toasting the sunset while savoring those immersive gulf views. The cool interior continues into an open chef's kitchen brimming with stainless appliances and custom cabinets. Gleaming granite countertops extend onto the lengthy breakfast bar; the perfect place to hang out and chat over drinks and snacks. Movie fans and sports lovers will appreciate the fully equipped home theater complete with a projection TV. The third floor is a tranquil sanctuary with a magnificent master suite that offers the ultimate gulf-front living. The updated ensuite boasts dual vanities, a walk-in shower and a free-standing tub for enjoying leisurely soaks. Two additional bedrooms (one furnished as a bunk room) are served by another full bathroom. This five-bedroom rental machine has been designed to maximize income. Recently updated, it offers $275,000 projected annual income, and has no HOA. World-class amenities include shopping, dining, golf and entertainment surrounding the resort and you're just a short hop from Silver Sands Outlet Mall.
